  "text": "We also performed compositional analysis of purified SMA-nanodiscs containing AqpZ, using Bradford and UV absorption protein assays, molybedenum blue phosphate assay and LC/MS lipid quantification, and UV absorption SMA quantification [CITATION_1] , (supplementary table S1 and S2). These analyses gave a composition by weight of 35.0 ± 1.0 % protein; 48.3 ± 1.5 % lipid; 16.3 ± 2.5 % SMA. This means that there are a considerable number of lipid molecules associated with each protein in a SMALP, about 140, representing multiple solvation layers.",
